♪♪♪

41:51.710 --> 41:53.141
EVERYTHING IS IN PLACE.

41:53.141 --> 41:55.213
WITH THE ULTIMATE POWER
TO DESTROY

41:55.213 --> 41:56.845
ALL THAT WE CHERISH MOST.

41:56.845 --> 41:59.287
SHALL WE PUT THE PLAN
TO A VOTE?

41:59.287 --> 42:01.890
(cell phone rings)

42:01.890 --> 42:03.822
(ring)

42:03.822 --> 42:05.824
(ring)

42:05.824 --> 42:07.525
(ring)

42:07.525 --> 42:09.127
(ring)

42:09.127 --> 42:10.198
(beep)

42:10.198 --> 42:12.100
VICTORIA.

42:12.100 --> 42:13.201
I'D LIKE TO SPEAK TO YOU

42:13.201 --> 42:14.663
ABOUT A MATTER
OF GRAVE IMPORTANCE.

42:14.663 --> 42:17.205
It's about Daniel.

42:17.205 --> 42:19.568
OH, I SEE YOU HAVE COMPANY.

42:19.568 --> 42:23.111
WHY DON'T YOU CALL ME
WHEN YOU'RE ALONE?

42:24.843 --> 42:26.014
(beep)

42:26.014 --> 42:28.316
WELL, THAT WAS UNEXPECTED.

42:28.316 --> 42:31.549
WHO WAS THAT?

42:31.549 --> 42:33.321
(sighs)

42:33.321 --> 42:35.624
LEVERAGE.
